":"Thankyou ，你戒左幾耐"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T18:29:21.000Z","msg":"有2個月啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n粥粉麵飯都冇食lu，有時一個星期cheat一餐<br />\n<br />\n不過聽講糖真係好毒，令皮膚老化得好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T18:31:57.000Z","msg":"巴打平時食咩？<br />\n營養夠唔夠？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T19:08:55.000Z","msg":"多數係屋企自己煮<br />\n因為出街食實在太難<br />\n你知香港樣樣都係配飯面 菜又無多條<br />\n<br />\n大部分時間係食青菜嚟填飽肚<br />\n其餘係蛋/肉同油 <br />\n<br />\n早餐食兩隻牛油煎蛋+大半碗菜（淋橄欖油/用豬油炒）<br />\n中午食一塊大雞扒連皮+大半碗菜（淋橄欖油）<br />\n晚餐食豉汁蒸排骨+菜（配排骨汁）<br />\n每日2L水<br />\n只要食夠油，就唔會好容易好快餓<br />\n<br />\n其實粥粉麵飯主要都係澱粉，<br />\n除咗提供熱量外，冇乜營養可言，<br />\n所以戒左都冇咩野，<br />\n起碼我個胸無降cup先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0025fc2867787c6dd5972147a757194508d7cff4","tid":931000,"uid":168104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fd23b31dbbe9e8c9c765400b50dd6ef1978ddd3","tid":931000,"uid":104511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c922a9523eb62c15a5d8e234364abc3d242a4ef","tid":931000,"uid":168104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66b70131fcdc4e684f26946e4894b1c7120711c9","tid":931000,"uid":104511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T18:31:06.000Z","msg":"咁你皮膚有無明顯好左？咁你平時淨係食菜同肉？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T18:35:04.000Z","msg":"係呀 不過我係為左減肥<br />\n每餐淨係食菜肉蛋 <br />\n瘦左一個size<br />\n<br />\n我覺得飲多啲水都係重點<br />\n樓主飲水飲得多唔多？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T18:42:27.000Z","msg":"好勁，你皮膚有好到？我唔抗拒飲水，不過飲得唔多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T19:10:16.000Z","msg":"其實我無咩留意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但戒糖點都係好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我幾年前開始飲甜野，肥撚左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgm